The paper deals with the asymptotic analysis of maximum a posteriori (MAP) estimators in compressed sensing, which involves linear measurements and Gaussian noise. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Signal Processing (cs.SP), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), or Systems and Control (cs.SI) sub-categories.
